      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, a bit standard though. Can you make it sound a little less like a template? I want it to feel a bit more personal so they know we actually valued their time, but keep it very professional. Maybe add a sentence about how we really liked their approach to problem-solving during the technical interview?",
